759774,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"833d23feac400a478c7282f631a9518f1266ab01","tid":1759774,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始要求救人加放人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"一個不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40731bff79f9556e86f2863f34454990dcfb494","tid":1759774,"uid":290694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"眼見連登一邊話立法會無可能過半, 立法會廢, 無用。我明。<br />\n<br />\n但係老豆豆講真係會有和理非, 會想係個制度裡面盡可能改變令普遍市民既聲音可以主導個政府。<br />\n<br />\n我亦都知好大部分人係堅信五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n首先係要政府回應、答應五大訴求先。<br />\n其中一項係真雙普選，如果做唔到依樣野，係唔可以一步到位做到從體制裡面改變香港。<br />\n但係淋病政府一直冷處理，一路拖，拖左我地半年依家先出個&lt;&lt;獨立&quot;檢討&quot;委員會&gt;&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n我個人無咁叻，我唔知道政府黎緊會點做。<br />\n我唔知個政府想拖我地幾耐。<br />\n政府唔回應、答應。我地就升級再升級。<br />\n就好似打緊一場長久而睇唔到終點既仗。<br />\n<br />\n但係立法會選舉下年黎緊，話長唔長，話短唔短，好快就到！<br />\n我地仲係到自己人屌自己人，做人都要有Plan A，Plan B。<br />\n點解仲唔可以停止爭論！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求我地要政府俾到交代我地，缺一不可。<br />\n立法會最基本野要做好，夠資格就登記做選民。<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，目標一致。<br />\n繼續high人權法、區議會，我睇唔到香港人出路！"},{"pid":"d353f2ea398ab16cff14ff917640128524a6e789","tid":1759774,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ea90135669e6805b2241aad4e0aff045a54d62","tid":1759774,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82125d17bf7a07babff8182ca1eebe46669ab282","tid":1759774,"uid":277640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"無人講？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMtev0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMtev0e.jpg&h=5eb974c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"CLS d黑警真係好賤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6501de552bccf7da20259424181e32c6caf53ee6","tid":1759774,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1ea90135669e6805b2241aad4e0aff045a54d62","tid":1759774,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82125d17bf7a07babff8182ca1eebe46669ab282","tid":1759774,"uid":277640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"無人講？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMtev0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMtev0e.jpg&h=5eb974c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"CLS d黑警真係好賤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:46:43.000Z","msg":"佢哋今日扮哂好人，話會人道處理，醫療需要行先，唔會大捜捕？我屌你啦，你前幾日扮人形狗入去拉哂啦！"}]}